			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Howdy all!
<br />

<br />
I am curious to see if anyone has a strat that they'd like to share in dropping this beastie. Many guildmates and friends want to take him down, but I have yet to see anything decent at allakhazam's for a strat, besides the bum rush tactic and rez/resend. I am only lvl 59 and will be 60 soon enough, but all my guildmates and friends attempting this are 65 and loaded with AA's. What tactics my a bard enter this with? I know the standard tune lineup for tanks overhaste, AC, ATK, DEX stackable DS, etc.., but am curious if someone has found another tactic that would work well. Not sure of what the group composition would be, but I would imagine two fairly well balanced groups of 60's and 65's.
<br />

<br />
Thanks in advance!
<br />

<br />
Wila from Torv</span></td>
