			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Clearing the caves is not necessary. You can either /duel or drag a mob to the bottom of the hill, and all die and consent an SoS rogue to drag through the caves, and bring to top. Or you can all duel at bottom, bard goes up top by a summon (charm a gator and send it against the horse up there, he will summon you up when charm breaks, then recharm and burn the gator, and chantkite the horse down.Either way is faster than clearing ther caves.
<br />

<br />
Ed</span></td>
