				<td colspan="2"><span>The strat above was a good one. I just wanna say make sure that everyone knows where the tunnel is. I was on a shade raid a while ago and it wiped pretty quickly because a guest didn't know where the tunnel was and ended up just wondering around a little under water, drawing aggro, and then worst of all finally found the tunnel and trained whoever had already made it, mostly the clerics, which left everyone else to either gate or die a hopeless death. After re-group we killed him.
<br />

<br />
I've only killed this guy once so maybe there are better ways, but we had all the druids and shammies chain-blast healing the tank(65 warrior), while 3 clerics were in cheal chain that was called as needed. Easy fight, dropped some specs and a nice bracer that i remember. </span></td>
